OL,6,FAlarm bells are being raised about
OL,7,FJersey's firearms legislation, with
OL,8,Fsome saying the laws are outdated and
OL,9,Fpotentially leave gaps in safety and
OL,10,Foversight.
OL,12,FFigures obtained by ITV News through a
OL,13,FFreedom of Information request reveal
OL,14,Fthere are more than 8,200 firearms in
OL,15,Fcirculation across the island, which
OL,16,Fworks out as one gun for every 12
OL,17,Fpeople.
