OL,6,FHowever, many own multiple weapons,
OL,7,Fshown by the fact that only 1,096
OL,8,Ffirearms certificates have been
OL,9,Fissued, which people must obtain
OL,10,Fbefore purchasing any gun or
OL,11,Fammunition.
OL,13,FWhilst the most popular include
OL,14,Ffirearms used for sport or hunting -
OL,15,Fsuch as pistols, rifles, and shotguns
OL,16,F- there are also bazookas, semi-
OL,17,Fautomatic rifles, muskets, and machine
OL,18,Fguns currently in circulation.
OL,20,FHow do you acquire a gun in Jersey?
