OL,6,FSome of the information provided may
OL,7,Fthen be checked against police and
OL,8,Fmedical records.
OL,10,FIt is the responsibility of the
OL,11,Ffirearm certificate holders to then
OL,12,Fuse and store guns safely and securely.
OL,14,FSome of the island's Parish Constables
OL,15,Fare raising concerns about this
OL,16,Fprocess, saying issuing gun licenses
OL,17,Fis one of the worst aspects of their
OL,18,Fjob because they do not always feel
OL,19,Fsufficiently qualified.
