OL,6,FThe Constable of St Lawrence, Deidre
OL,7,FMezbourian, says she has concerns that
OL,8,Feach certificate is issued for five
OL,9,Fyears "with no additional checks".
OL,11,FShe adds: "We go through quite a lot
OL,12,Fof due diligence before deciding
OL,13,Fwhether someone is fit to hold a
OL,14,Ffirearm certificate. However, from the
OL,15,Fmoment they receive it, we don't have
OL,16,Fany connection with them for that five-
OL,17,Fyear duration.
