OL,6,F"So there are no checks on their
OL,7,Fsecurity, checks on whether they have
OL,8,Fmanaged to acquire an unauthorised
OL,9,Ffirearm, and there are no medical
OL,10,Fchecks."
OL,12,FThe laws have not been updated in
OL,13,FJersey in 25 years - despite repeated
OL,14,Fpromises from a series of recent Home
OL,15,FAffairs Ministers that a full review
OL,16,Fwould take place.
OL,18,FThe island's Constables are now
OL,19,Frenewing their calls for an urgent
OL,20,Fassessment.
